			<td width="100%" height="25">
				<table width="100%" cellspacing="0">
				<tr>
				
					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p141259">Re: SNES audio hardware info</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=141259#p141259"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Sun Feb 15, 2015 1:03 pm&nbsp;</div></td>
				</tr>
